{{cite news | title = TOWKAY LOKE YEW, C.M.G., L.L.D. | publisher= 海峽時報 | date = 1917年1月5日 | url = http://eresources.nlb.gov.sg/newspapers/Digitised/Article/straitstimes19170105-1.2.51.aspx?q=%22LOKE+YEW%22&mode=advanced&f_df=19170101&f_dt=19171231&page=1&sort=oldest&token=yew%2cloke&sessionid=106654d64e3b46aabddac2c934c66649 }} </ref>。
